com.rigado.rigablue

Interface IRigCoreListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RigCoreBluetooth

    public interface IRigCoreListener
    This interface listens to events coming directly from the low level Bluetooth interface on Android. It should not be directly implemented by applications using Rigablue.
